Title: Part 4: The Mines of Moria
Text:
The long darkness of Moria...
Not a save place, but we have to go through here.

I hope we can make it through the mines unnoticed.
If the legends are true, it could be dangerous...
CompleteText:
There is an exit! Finally daylight again!

It's no time to mourn Gandalf, when it gets dark the place just swarms with orcs.We should go fast to Lothlorien.
